\f3\i\b \cf4 \cb3 Addition of HCN to ethanal\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0\b0 \cf4 \cb3 The reaction again starts with a nucleophilic attack by the cyanide ion on the slightly positive carbon atom.\
\
Reaction is completed by the addition of a hydrogen ion from a hydrogen cyanide molecule, to form 2-hydroxypropanenitrile.\
